camping ground
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a specific place where sheep gather, usually on a rise, in the evening.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:sheep camp
Pronunciation:
