Citations
Date: 0/0/1873
Source: Station Amusements in NZ
Author: BARKER
Vol / Page: 4
Edition:
Quote: On the skyline of the hills could be preceived towards evening, mobs of sheep feeding with their heads up-wind and travelling to the high camping-grounds which they always select in preference to a valley.
